<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>FOUNTAIN OF LIFE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Luinak a um, thisan a luong,
 Kalvari a pawt chuh;
 Gilote di'n zie luipi chuh;
 Gitloh thienna ahi.

[V2]
 Aw, kalvari lui hawih tak (3)
 Kei di'n na hung luong dawk.

[V3]
 2. Gilo, thi ding khetdenpa khan,
 Thienna lui chuh a mu'i;
 Amah bangin gilo mahleng,
 Ei hih thiengtho thei hi.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa deihtak, Na thisan lun,
 Zatam in a he puou;
 Hukdamte chun ziehi a muu,
 A puokgik kilik mang.

[V5]
 4. Ginnan hinna lui chuh ka mu'i,
 A luong ka gam chanin;
 Ei hehpihna ka thupi pen,
 Ka thihna geiin le.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>115</hymn_number>
</song>